SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE

Input Symptoms → Data Processing → Machine Learning Model → Disease Prediction → Output Result

MODULES

1. Dataset Collection

Collects disease and symptom data for training.

2. Data Preprocessing

Cleans and transforms the dataset into a suitable format.

3. Model Training

Trains the machine learning algorithm using historical data.

4. Prediction Module

Accepts symptoms and predicts the corresponding disease.

5. Result Display

Displays the predicted disease to the user.

