CONCLUSION

The Disease Prediction System is an effective machine learning application that predicts diseases based on symptoms. It provides quick and reliable preliminary results and can support healthcare professionals and users in early disease detection. With further improvements and larger datasets, the system can become a valuable tool in modern healthcare.
